name: Tahir Tribal Mask
description:
A cosmic explosion caused it's creation.
In its heart a sonic boom.
The love call it makes, is a sign of prosperity and growth.
There is no essence as strong as what it beholds.
It will render idle thought vacant.
Soullessness is quenched in one.
The Spirit of Tahir ushers in a new wave of kindness.
A new wave of hope and vision that may never be impaired.
